sentences: Rio Okano (岡野 里音 Okano Rio, born on March 5, 1991 in Kobe, Japan), also known as Rionos, is a Japanese singer, songwriter, music producer, and voice actress.
She entered Osaka University of Arts in 2009 as a correspondence student.
Her condition improved, so she attended computer music school Dee in Osaka in the autumn of 2009.

It was released on CD in 2013.
In 2016, Lantis's producer Junnosuke Sato listened to her songs for Yufu and contacted her.
She made her major debut from Lantis in 2017 in the anime's ending theme "Hashitairo".
In the Märchen Mädchen anime of the following year, she composed background music in addition to ending theme.
